      <title>由于利率前景减弱中东风险和美国寒潮，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于红海新的不稳定和美国寒流扰乱了产量，而更广泛市场的疲软基调抵消了油价小幅走低的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 23:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
